{"article_id":"ks0CLeQHszAXYK3C","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Shortly after landing back in the United States Wednesday morning on the heels of successful trip to India ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump announced","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he will hold a press conference this evening about the coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Just landed .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"India was great ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"trip very successful .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Heading to the White House .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Meetings and calls scheduled today .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"@ CDCgov , @ SecAzar and all doing a great job with respect to Coronavirus !","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Briefing this afternoon .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"February 26 , 2020","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"I will be having a News Conference at the White House , on this subject , today at 6:00 P.M.","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"CDC representatives , and others , will be there .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Thank you !","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"February 26 , 2020","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Yesterday the CDC noted","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"while there is currently no community spread of coronavirus ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Americans should be prepared for disruption of everyday life","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"when it arrives .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Now is the time","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"for US businesses , hospitals , and communities to begin preparing for the possible spread of # COVID19 .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"CDC continues to work with business , education & healthcare sectors ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"encouraging employers to be prepared .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Learn more :","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"https : //t.co/OUYvMhdIaS .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"- CDC","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"( @ CDCgov )","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"February 25 , 2020","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Overseas in China ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"where the pandemic started ,","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"nearly 1800 people have died .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"Iran has the second highest mortality rate","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"with more than fifty people succumbing to the disease .","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"During a press conference at the State Department Tuesday , Secretary Mike Pompeo condemned China for the unnecessary spread of the virus due to communist government 's secrecy and censorship .","depth":2},{"id":39,"text":"`` We want to applaud the brave reporters","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"who are covering the spread of coronavirus from Wuhan itself .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Expelling our journalists , exposes once again the [ Chinese ] government 's issue","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that led to SARS and now the coronavirus ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"namely censorship .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"It can have deadly consequences , ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"`` Had China permitted its own and foreign journalists and medical personnel to speak and investigate freely","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"Chinese officials and other nations would have been far better prepared to address the challenge .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Similarly , the United States is deeply concerned by information","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"indicating","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"the Iranian regime may have suppressed vital details about the outbreak in that country .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"As of yesterday afternoon Iran was second only to China in coronavirus deaths . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":89,"right":102,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":84,"right":88,"relation":"context","